- Create namespace ingress-nginx
# kubectl create ns ingress-nginx

- Install Nginx Ingress Controller
# kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/controller-v1.3.0/deploy/static/provider/cloud/deploy.yaml

- Check the ingress controller  all is running 
# kubectl get all -n ingress-nginx
https://github.com/tux40/onboard-pretest/issues/1#issue-1764611185
- Pointing Domain From DNS Server To IP External Ingress Controller
